    "Id": 7,
    "Content": "\n### Environment Variables\n\n| Variable | Default | Description |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` | (required) | Your Anthropic API key |\n| `CLAUDE_MODEL` | `claude-sonnet-4-6` | Model to use |\n| `CLAUDE_MAX_TOKENS` | `8192` | Max output tokens |\n| `ANTHROPIC_API_URL` | `https://api.anthropic.com` | API base URL |\n| `CLAUDE_SH_PERMISSIONS` | `ask` | Permission mode: `ask`, `allow`, or `deny` |\n\n### Commands\n",
    "ContentSha": "OBM51Oi00/PiKjERXMs67M2Yt8ehudYbD16XwqG2FdE=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "### 환경 변수\n\n| 변수 | 기본값 | 설명 |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` | (필수) | 당신의 Anthropic API 키 |\n| `CLAUDE_MODEL` | `claude-sonnet-4-6` | 사용할 모델 |\n| `CLAUDE_MAX_TOKENS` | `8192` | 최대 출력 토큰 수 |\n| `ANTHROPIC_API_URL` | `https://api.anthropic.com` | API 기본 URL |\n| `CLAUDE_SH_PERMISSIONS` | `ask` | 권한 모드: `ask`, `allow`, 또는 `deny` |\n\n### 명령어\n\n",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [
